name: WorkoutTracker
headerTaglineTwo: WorkoutTracker is your all-in-one dashboard to log workouts and meals, track your progress in real time, and stay motivated on your fitness journey.

services.title: Workout Tracker
services.description: Our workout tracker lets you effortlessly log every exercise, from strength training and cardio sessions to yoga and Pilates. Customize your routines by selecting from a library of exercises or creating your own, record sets, reps, and weights, and track duration and intensity for each session. Built-in timers and rest-period alerts keep you on schedule, while interactive progress charts highlight your improvements in strength, endurance, and flexibility over time.

services.title: Meal Tracker
services.description: The meal tracker and calorie counter make nutritional logging a breeze. Each meal entry automatically calculates calories, protein, carbs, fats, and more, and visualizes your daily intake against your personalized goals. Weekly nutrition summaries and trend graphs help you fine-tune your diet for better energy, weight management, and overall health.
